  - Use the established error handling patterns
  - Implement proper loading states
  - Use the toast notification system for user feedback
  - Handle network errors gracefully
  - Follow the established retry patterns

  # Loading States
  - Use the established loading state patterns
  - Implement proper loading indicators
  - Use the established loading message patterns
  - Follow the established loading state management

  # API Service Patterns
  - Create service functions for API calls
  - Use proper error handling in service functions
  - Implement proper response transformation
  - Use the established service patterns

  # Request Configuration
  - Use proper request headers and authentication
  - Implement proper request timeout handling
  - Use the established request configuration patterns
